{"tid":2289197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【用心良苦】日本課「金」GAME 每日告知女角屎屎情況 真正目的是…","createTime":"2020-11-17T05:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T07:01:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f6db27f98f36c9acc7f18d41f5f860e098353205","tid":2289197,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E8%89%AF%E8%8B%A6-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%AA%B2-%E9%87%91-game-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E5%A5%B3%E8%A7%92%E5%B1%8E%E5%B1%8E%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2589%25AF%25E8%258B%25A6-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E9%2587%2591-game-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%25B1%258E%25E5%25B1%258E%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581-%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM41xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=bbb73003\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2589%25AF%25E8%258B%25A6-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25AA%25B2-%25E9%2587%2591-game-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%25B1%258E%25E5%25B1%258E%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581-%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%259B%25AE%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2598%25AF%2F&h=a2621be6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/personal/%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E8%89%AF%E8%8B%A6-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%AA%B2-%E9%87%91-game-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%91%8A%E7%9F%A5%E5%A5%B3%E8%A7%92%E5%B1%8E%E5%B1%8E%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF/</a><br />\n<br />\n這隻在日本新近推出的遊戲名為 UNKORE（UNKO 是日文屎屎的意思）。一如大多數課金 GAME，你可以免費在遊戲世界穿行，但若想要心儀的角色和道具，你就需要「課」，不是「課」現金，而是「課」屎屎的「金」。也不需要你真的把屎屎送過去，只要向遊戲中的女孩子們報告你的屎屎情況就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，屎屎就是屎屎，有甚麼好報告的。但世屎並唔係你諗得咁簡單。首先顏色就有好多種，黃土色、茶色、焦茶色、黑色、紅色、綠色、灰白色（？有的嗎？）然後還有質地。水狀、泥狀、香蕉狀、芋狀，等等。<br />\n<br />\n然後你問，為甚麼要報告呢，阿叔開頭以為是科學家收集數據，但原來不是，這是日本屎屎學會（日本 UNKO 學會）用心良苦的一著，因為人透過屎屎可以推測出腸胃健康，你向女孩報告屎屎，學會就可以在你身體可能有毛病時，提早叫你睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n講返隻遊戲啦，只要你向可愛的女孩報告屎屎情況，就可以換取裝備等等，用來對抗遊戲世界（地圖好似消化道）裡面的敵人（有害細菌、腫瘤等）。順帶一提，那些關心你屎屎的女孩子，其實是擬人化的有益細菌等等的東東。她們的命名也都與屎屎有關，如這個叫 Anri Hartmann 的 19 歲女劍士，姓名讀音就和著名的法國醫生 Henri Hartmann 相同。<br />\n<br />\n所以別以為這是不文遊戲，是真的好有心的遊戲。可惜香港暫仍未有得下載，香港玩家要用「其他方法」了。（唔好問我咩方法）<br />\n<br />\n官方網站﹕<a href=\"https://unkore.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funkore.jp%2F&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM41xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=550ad129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unkore.jp/</a>"},{"pid":"f5b6868551bf66457881d9e04c5dd007432d1ebe","tid":2289197,"uid":302471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b7fcf3030fafab41a561e481fa09f56ceccc28","tid":2289197,"uid":438,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"真 糞game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c134d301c9d5ec81f84c5a041b284ef21cd089a9","tid":2289197,"uid":85461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"仆街仔<br />\n你好玩唔玩<br />\n玩屎!?"},{"pid":"d21f7c5c026217193834e6ce934dee8d18c6c73a","tid":2289197,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"我食緊飯架..."},{"pid":"2af8620b5a44e9ebee916cb7df9bb50992c725ca","tid":2289197,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac